title: Julia Fischer - J.S. Bach Violin Concertos (musicfromrizzo)
description:
Julia Roberts and the  Academy of St. Martin in the Fields ensemble give us
a lovely rendition of my most favourite pieces from Bach and Vivaldi too -
The Bach Concertos for violin 1 and 2 (there's other music pieces from Bach
here as well - lovely) and we also get just a couple of minutes sample from
Vivaldi's Four Seasons - which we have uploaded here in full by the greatest group
I Musici of Italy featuring Roberto Michelucci on violin. (thanks to all the greatest
folk who have been seeding this for us). 
My favourite movement is "Winter" in Vivaldi's most famous "Four Seasons" music composition

Our best offering of The Four Seasons by Antonio Vivaldi done by the best group
(I Musici) is posted here as well

enjoy the music - with thanks - grazie - danke and merci equally!

Michael Rizzo Chessman
(musicfromrizzo)
